# Session [19] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Static IP Routing chist?  
- Tarze kar static routing  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – Static Routing Basics
- Static Routing = meghdar dadan route ha **manual** be router  
- Routers address ro nemifahmand → admin moshakhas mikonad masir  

## Explanation

### Tarze Kar
- Har route ba **destination network + subnet mask + next hop/router IP** moshakhas mishavad  
- Router packet ro be masir mored nazar mifrestad  
- Command dar Windows/Router: `route add [destination] mask [subnet] [next hop]`  

### Estefadeh-ha
- Networks koochik va simple  
- Jaye ke traffic predictable ast  
- Resource kam (no CPU load)  

### Example
| Destination | Subnet Mask | Next Hop | Interface |
|------------|------------|----------|-----------|
| 192.168.2.0 | 255.255.255.0 | 192.168.1.2 | Ethernet0 |
| 10.0.5.0   | 255.0.0.0     | 10.0.0.1   | Ethernet1 |

